  "3126670": {
    "name": "Lokko Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3126670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/fa1a46cffb8966a2474d1230e1cffcd7.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/fa1a46cffb8966a2474d1230e1cffcd7.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/fa1a46cffb8966a2474d1230e1cffcd7.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是 LOKKO 的演示版本，包含有限的关卡和功能。 </strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong>LOKKO</strong> 是一款独特的 3D 平台游戏，在这里乐趣与创造力相遇。玩家可在 <strong>PS5®</strong>、<strong>PC</strong> 和 <strong>iOS</strong> 上无缝、实时地创建并分享具有挑战性的关卡。创建你的头像，设计属于你的敌人和 Boss。充分利用 <strong>DualSense™</strong> 在三大平台上的强大功能。玩家可以交易自己的创作并相互竞争。成为那个打造出最有趣、最独特、最具创意关卡的人。<strong>LOKKO</strong> 入选了 <strong>India Hero Project</strong> 第二期。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/Breakline_LOKKO_StorePage.png?t=1759563675\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/e4dfb6d5b1db6321e8a4b42e31fc1e50.webp?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关卡编辑器</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/75d6b84a41b53e76589dccef8e535824.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/75d6b84a41b53e76589dccef8e535824.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/75d6b84a41b53e76589dccef8e535824.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过我们内置的平台关卡编辑器，玩家可以生成并分享自己的关卡。通过连接计时器、加速器和开关，放置 NPC 和 Boss，打造有趣的关卡，与朋友一起畅玩。支持游戏手柄以及键盘/鼠标，操作简单直观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>角色编辑器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/8e16b49c5ece8f9162c005fc04acd5c8.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/8e16b49c5ece8f9162c005fc04acd5c8.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/8e16b49c5ece8f9162c005fc04acd5c8.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置角色编辑器让你可以无限定制可玩角色。通过删除、添加、上色方块改变外观，使用简便的控制进行编辑。将更改直接应用到所有单人关卡，并可一键分享你的自定义关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>NPC 编辑器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/c5e06fb52906cabada54202500b773a8.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/c5e06fb52906cabada54202500b773a8.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/c5e06fb52906cabada54202500b773a8.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过添加、删除、上色方块来改变所有 NPC 敌人的外观与行为。立即将其替换进关卡编辑器，查看它们在游戏与用户自制关卡中的表现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/Breakline_LOKKO_StorePage.png?t=1759563675\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/227b00e9d03e11500d652810b24d6a7c.webp?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/794d570ee9876962a817530eebf08eee.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/794d570ee9876962a817530eebf08eee.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/794d570ee9876962a817530eebf08eee.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持手柄的本地双人模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/Breakline_LOKKO_StorePage.png?t=1759563675\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/ea0a7d0a1db30c2c32b9d1ee2ec693b5.webp?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/51e8f5474f468c5b1c74aa504a49da6d.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/51e8f5474f468c5b1c74aa504a49da6d.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/51e8f5474f468c5b1c74aa504a49da6d.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lokko 让各个年龄段的玩家都能在 <strong>Steam Deck</strong>™ 上协作、创造与游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/Breakline_LOKKO_StorePage.png?t=1759563675\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/a48a581dea8c9c3fde8aa0c002504f02.webp?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/ffd88b88ba68a0f30b226fbdc96785a8.poster.avif?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/ffd88b88ba68a0f30b226fbdc96785a8.webm?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/ffd88b88ba68a0f30b226fbdc96785a8.mp4?t=1759563675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lokko 支持 DualSense™ 无线手柄、Xbox 无线手柄，以及鼠标与键盘进行协作、创作与游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/Breakline_LOKKO_StorePage.png?t=1759563675\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/6b760691b47c2cb953ed5aa2b5a80285.webp?t=1759563675\" width=600 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126670/extras/INTRO_STORY_GIF.gif?t=1759563675\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lokko 和他的哥哥 Lokko Sr. 经营着一家名为 Lokko Pizza 的小披萨店。他们制作世界上最好吃的披萨，并把热腾腾的披萨送到世界任何角落。无论是甜美的 Hawaiian Surprise，还是芝士满满的 Sicilian Special，都能送到饥肠辘辘的顾客手中。然而，在城镇的另一边，由 Goobol 及其爪牙领导的邪恶快餐公司正竭尽全力阻止 Lokko 送披萨。Goobol 一心只做廉价而糟糕的食物。一旦阻止了 Lokko，世界将被迫吃他们的冷冻加工食品。Lokko 将奔跑、驾驶，甚至穿越时空，为你送上一份新鲜可口的披萨。 </p>",
